  {
    "key": "33ad1f8fd40d9e46a8538442c1c8bdfb6801dc23186c72e8bb3139334e1a5394",
    "original": "[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You come across the once-caravan hand, %caravanhand%, finicking with the company wagon. He's nailing a slat of board to the bed and using pins to put it on a roller. The board can then drop down into the belly of the wagon with a little bit of a pull and switch. Rather ingenious. This will allow you to load more onto the wagon.",
    "translation": "",
    "context": "Text = \"[img]gfx/ui/events/event_55.png[/img]You come across the once-caravan hand, %caravanhand%, finicking with the company wagon. He's nailing a slat of board to the bed and using pins to put it on a roller. The board can then drop down into the belly of the wagon with a little bit of a pull and switch. Rather ingenious. This will allow you to load more onto the wagon.\""
